
Overview of noun chopper

The noun chopper has 4 senses (first 1 from tagged texts)
                                        
1. (1) chop, chopper -- (a grounder that bounces high in the air)
2. chopper, pearly -- (informal terms for a human `tooth')
3. helicopter, chopper, whirlybird, eggbeater -- (an aircraft without wings that obtains its lift from the rotation of overhead blades)
4. cleaver, meat cleaver, chopper -- (a butcher's knife having a large square blade)
